# Shell scripts must use LF line endings so they run under bash/dash on
# Linux, WSL, and macOS even when the repo is checked out or edited on
# Windows. CRLF here breaks `set -euo pipefail` (read as `pipefail\r`) and
# corrupts every other line, which silently broke the GGML native build and
# the CUDA arch-detection fallback.
*.sh text eol=lf
